<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.2">
<l>vaṟṟā mutunī roṭumālvarai yēḻum</l>
<l>tuṟṟā kamuṉtuṟ ṟiyatolpuka ḻōṉē</l>
<l>yaṟṟē ṉaṭiyē ṉuṉṉaiyēyaḻaik kiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>peṟṟē ṉaruḷtan tiṭuveṉentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One of ancient fame who once gulped, like a [rice] ball,</l>
<l>The seven massive mountains along with the primordial seas which never dry,</l>
<l>I am ruined; I, your servant, am calling you.</l>
<l>Once and for all, grant [your] grace to me who is worthy, my father, lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
